WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Subtitles by DramaFever

2
00:00:06.653 --> 00:00:09.078
<i>[Episode 14]</i>

3
00:00:09.078 --> 00:00:13.401
<i>[Min Yi Bok - Not Read
Ji Hong Ah - Not Read]</i>

4
00:00:15.038 --> 00:00:18.025
Aren't you going to eat, Hyun Soo?

5
00:00:18.993 --> 00:00:21.729
You're the only person who read
the script for episode 9.

6
00:00:21.729 --> 00:00:24.772
I saw the location
where they're shooting today

7
00:00:24.772 --> 00:00:27.926
and it is not where you set episode 8.

8
00:00:29.232 --> 00:00:32.522
It's because it's always somewhere else
that it doesn't seem realistic.

9
00:00:33.470 --> 00:00:35.385
They're all so busy
with the shoot

10
00:00:35.385 --> 00:00:38.137
that's probably why they didn't have
time to read the next episode.

11
00:00:38.137 --> 00:00:41.092
Let's eat something delicious
and get our spirits up.

12
00:00:41.762 --> 00:00:44.070
I made the reservation.

13
00:00:44.070 --> 00:00:45.732
You pay, Soo Hyun.

14
00:00:45.732 --> 00:00:47.760
It's kind of an expensive place.

15
00:00:51.662 --> 00:00:54.287
You always know how to
make me feel better.

16
00:01:02.516 --> 00:01:04.200
Hello.

17
00:01:04.200 --> 00:01:05.337
Yes, hello.

18
00:01:05.337 --> 00:01:06.849
Allow me to escort you to your seat.

19
00:01:08.801 --> 00:01:10.581
Have you been here before, Hyun Soo?

20
00:01:10.581 --> 00:01:13.471
How did you think of
making a reservation here?

21
00:01:13.471 --> 00:01:15.824
Because it seemed to me
that you wanted to come here.

22
00:01:15.824 --> 00:01:18.455
You asked me about
Chef Ohn Jung Seon last time.

23
00:01:20.468 --> 00:01:24.497
I love you to the stars
and back, Kyung.

24
00:01:24.497 --> 00:01:25.655
Really?

25
00:01:29.557 --> 00:01:31.486
Is the sea bream okay today, Ha Sung?

26
00:01:31.486 --> 00:01:32.486
Yes, Chef!

27
00:01:32.486 --> 00:01:33.956
Make sure you get the temperature right.

28
00:01:33.958 --> 00:01:34.958
Yes, Chef.

29
00:01:37.060 --> 00:01:39.229
Table four, two lunch courses.

30
00:01:39.229 --> 00:01:40.533
We'll be serving them their
amuse-bouche soon

31
00:01:40.533 --> 00:01:41.899
so put the fish in early!

32
00:01:41.899 --> 00:01:43.075
- Yes, Sir!
- Yes, Sir!

33
00:01:43.804 --> 00:01:45.494
Excuse me, Chef.

34
00:01:45.494 --> 00:01:49.078
The order that just came in is
for Writer Lee Hyun Soo's table.

35
00:01:58.215 --> 00:01:59.771
Isn't it really delicious?

36
00:02:00.477 --> 00:02:02.801
It's a good thing I brought you here.

37
00:02:02.801 --> 00:02:05.667
You look so happy while you're eating.

38
00:02:07.581 --> 00:02:09.741
I'm just living in the moment.

39
00:02:10.378 --> 00:02:13.184
Because I don't know when I'll be
happy again when this moment passes.

40
00:02:14.856 --> 00:02:16.421
Hearing that makes me too sad.

41
00:02:16.421 --> 00:02:18.981
It sounds as if misfortune will
strike again almost immediately.

42
00:02:21.904 --> 00:02:23.278
Did you enjoy your meal?

43
00:02:28.369 --> 00:02:30.398
Oh.

44
00:02:30.398 --> 00:02:32.469
How did you know I was here?

45
00:02:33.161 --> 00:02:35.820
Oh... you're close with him, aren't you?

46
00:02:35.820 --> 00:02:38.344
Seeing as how you're using informal
speech with each other.

47
00:02:38.344 --> 00:02:41.551
Yeah. This is mu junior,
whom I love.

48
00:02:45.354 --> 00:02:47.113
Oh, Hyun Soo!

49
00:02:48.274 --> 00:02:49.504
Why are you getting up?

50
00:02:49.504 --> 00:02:50.974
I'm going to go.

51
00:02:50.974 --> 00:02:53.320
You won't need to work
on your script, so just go home.

52
00:02:53.320 --> 00:02:54.452
Your place is close by.

53
00:02:54.452 --> 00:02:56.391
I'll go to the studio
and monitor the situation

54
00:02:56.391 --> 00:02:57.917
and I'll call you if anything changes.

55
00:02:57.917 --> 00:02:59.065
Goodbye.

56
00:03:02.267 --> 00:03:04.733
Why... is she being like that?

57
00:03:04.733 --> 00:03:07.940
I think she's telling you to
stay here longer.

58
00:03:10.631 --> 00:03:12.574
You've never been to my place, right?

59
00:03:33.687 --> 00:03:35.941
You can't sit still because
you're so curious, huh?

60
00:03:35.941 --> 00:03:37.191
How'd you know?

61
00:03:41.364 --> 00:03:42.846
Wow, this smells great.

62
00:03:42.846 --> 00:03:44.578
It's Blue Mountain coffee.

63
00:03:44.578 --> 00:03:47.205
Not even you can afford it,
since it's too expensive.

64
00:03:47.205 --> 00:03:49.088
I received this as a gift.

65
00:03:51.188 --> 00:03:53.899
All right, my ears are open now.

66
00:03:57.040 --> 00:03:59.894
If you're wondering whether you should
tell me or not, just tell me.

67
00:04:03.211 --> 00:04:05.900
I heard from Hong Ah...

68
00:04:05.900 --> 00:04:08.168
about you and her.

69
00:04:09.043 --> 00:04:12.487
Tell me exactly what you heard, so
there's no room for misunderstanding.

70
00:04:12.487 --> 00:04:15.428
How are you so resolute
and stoic all the time?

71
00:04:16.545 --> 00:04:18.520
I've rarely seen you
lose your cool.

72
00:04:18.520 --> 00:04:22.103
You're so sure of your goals and
you don't care about what others think.

73
00:04:22.103 --> 00:04:24.032
I really envy you.

74
00:04:30.222 --> 00:04:33.619
I have nobody to catch me
if I stumble and fall.

75
00:04:34.199 --> 00:04:36.956
I don't have the luxury to stumble.

76
00:04:37.848 --> 00:04:40.432
So there's no need for you
to be envious of me.

77
00:04:41.603 --> 00:04:43.949
I feel like Hong Ah and I
are fighting over a guy

78
00:04:43.949 --> 00:04:45.477
and it makes me uncomfortable.

79
00:04:47.567 --> 00:04:49.287
Give up on me, then.

80
00:04:51.629 --> 00:04:54.787
If you like me so little that you can
give up on me, then just give up now.

81
00:04:57.619 --> 00:05:00.737
I loathe causing any emotional
distress in anyone.

82
00:05:00.737 --> 00:05:04.328
I never once caused you
emotional distress while we dated.

83
00:05:05.742 --> 00:05:09.711
So, Ms. Lee Hyun Soo, who says,
"humans are insignificant."

84
00:05:10.728 --> 00:05:14.588
Ms. Lee Hyun Soo, who pushes away the
man who loves her, because of reality.

85
00:05:16.944 --> 00:05:19.867
What reason can you give
me for us to start over?

86
00:05:22.847 --> 00:05:24.496
I'm sorry.

87
00:05:28.485 --> 00:05:30.261
I'm scared.

88
00:05:31.307 --> 00:05:33.859
There's no reason that a woman who
dumped me once

89
00:05:33.859 --> 00:05:36.615
couldn't dump me again.

90
00:05:40.538 --> 00:05:42.658
Reality is always harsh.

91
00:06:00.650 --> 00:06:02.865
I thought about only you.

92
00:06:03.795 --> 00:06:07.775
Love is something that two people share,
but I thought only about myself.

93
00:06:12.100 --> 00:06:14.105
I treated it too lightly.

94
00:06:25.184 --> 00:06:27.386
I'll think about it.

95
00:06:45.198 --> 00:06:46.817
Congratulations.

96
00:06:46.817 --> 00:06:50.025
I said I'd come to you,
so why did you come here?

97
00:06:50.025 --> 00:06:52.514
I don't have a single moment
to waste by sitting down.

98
00:06:52.514 --> 00:06:54.357
I want to hurry up and leave.

99
00:06:55.716 --> 00:06:59.439
I want to hurry up and see my
dreams become reality.

100
00:07:01.901 --> 00:07:05.355
Well, if you've been chosen as
a winner for HNC's open call

101
00:07:05.355 --> 00:07:08.419
you'll be contracted to work with
HNC for five years.

102
00:07:08.997 --> 00:07:12.540
It'll be difficult for us to collaborate
with you on this project.

103
00:07:12.540 --> 00:07:16.905
Why do you think I chose your production
company among the many out there?

104
00:07:17.823 --> 00:07:21.222
All right, let's give this
some consideration.

105
00:07:22.078 --> 00:07:25.134
Have you read my script yet?

106
00:07:25.134 --> 00:07:28.431
It was a nice, easy read,
which was nice.

107
00:07:28.431 --> 00:07:33.465
Things like birth secrets and conflicts
between the rich and poor never get old.

108
00:07:34.965 --> 00:07:36.186
That's what I was going for.

109
00:07:36.186 --> 00:07:39.662
Most of the characters in there are
based on the people I know.

110
00:07:39.662 --> 00:07:42.220
It'll be more realistic
than other TV shows.

111
00:07:42.703 --> 00:07:45.879
Let's think about whether we should
sign a contract or not.

112
00:07:45.879 --> 00:07:47.617
If we do sign a contract,
what I want

113
00:07:47.617 --> 00:07:50.153
is for you to pay me more than Hyun Soo,
even by just 10 won.

114
00:07:51.083 --> 00:07:52.961
That will be difficult.

115
00:07:52.961 --> 00:07:54.828
It's because of your
personal feelings, right?

116
00:07:55.501 --> 00:07:57.686
- It's because you like her...
- Ms. Ji Hong Ah.

117
00:08:00.513 --> 00:08:02.228
Writer Ji Hong Ah.

118
00:08:02.228 --> 00:08:06.008
There are some rules you need to follow
if you want to work with me.

119
00:08:06.948 --> 00:08:09.686
First, you must mind your manners.

120
00:08:11.395 --> 00:08:14.413
Writer Lee started as a
winner for an open call

121
00:08:14.413 --> 00:08:17.420
and then got great reviews on the
show she wrote after that.

122
00:08:18.674 --> 00:08:22.035
You're nowhere near that level yet.

123
00:08:22.035 --> 00:08:24.681
Hyun Soo wrote a one-act.

124
00:08:24.681 --> 00:08:26.631
But I won with an episodic script.

125
00:08:26.631 --> 00:08:28.287
Writing a TV show isn't about the words.

126
00:08:28.287 --> 00:08:30.655
They're judged by whether or not
they make it on the air.

127
00:08:54.884 --> 00:08:56.711
Yes, CEO Park?

128
00:08:56.711 --> 00:08:58.533
What are you up to?

129
00:08:59.486 --> 00:09:02.658
Um... thinking.

130
00:09:02.658 --> 00:09:04.063
Thinking?
As if.

131
00:09:04.063 --> 00:09:07.980
Come out. Thinking too much at a time
like this will only make your head hurt.

132
00:09:07.980 --> 00:09:09.081
It's better to take a walk.

133
00:09:24.754 --> 00:09:26.318
It's not here.

134
00:09:26.865 --> 00:09:29.721
It headed back inside after
doing what it needed to do.

135
00:09:29.722 --> 00:09:31.461
It's not dead?

136
00:09:33.127 --> 00:09:35.600
Flowers bloom according
to the season, you know.

137
00:09:37.759 --> 00:09:41.072
Its season passed, so it'll
rest and come back out again.

138
00:09:48.380 --> 00:09:51.514
I didn't know you had a side
like this, CEO Park.

139
00:09:51.514 --> 00:09:52.634
What kind of side?

140
00:09:53.206 --> 00:09:56.413
Being warm?
Being shy?

141
00:09:56.797 --> 00:09:59.755
Why did you start thinking that?

142
00:10:00.922 --> 00:10:04.459
Someone threw a bomb at me again.

143
00:10:04.928 --> 00:10:07.412
You wanted me to be prepared
before I was hit

144
00:10:07.412 --> 00:10:09.890
and you wanted to
show me how to be strong

145
00:10:09.890 --> 00:10:14.211
and make sure I knew that life goes on,
or something like that, right?

146
00:10:15.653 --> 00:10:17.394
Something like that.

147
00:10:20.081 --> 00:10:25.036
Ms. Hong Ah came to see me
not too long ago, with her work.

148
00:10:25.036 --> 00:10:26.923
And I met with her today, too.

149
00:10:27.533 --> 00:10:28.774
What did she say?

150
00:10:28.774 --> 00:10:30.350
She wanted to sign a contract with me.

151
00:10:30.884 --> 00:10:32.817
Are you going to do it?

152
00:10:32.817 --> 00:10:34.749
I'm on the fence about it.

153
00:10:36.055 --> 00:10:39.005
Half of me really likes the
script because it's good.

154
00:10:39.005 --> 00:10:41.495
But another half of me feels like
her personality is too much.

155
00:10:43.461 --> 00:10:45.658
What does her personality matter?

156
00:10:45.658 --> 00:10:47.326
It's not like you'll be living with her.

157
00:10:48.943 --> 00:10:50.721
Why, are you going to live with her?

158
00:10:51.576 --> 00:10:53.044
No.

159
00:10:53.044 --> 00:10:55.461
Then just do as you always do.

160
00:10:59.637 --> 00:11:03.095
Wow, the sky is so beautiful.

161
00:11:04.182 --> 00:11:07.534
It's been a while since I've gotten
such a nice look at the sky.

162
00:11:07.534 --> 00:11:10.279
The sky really is pretty.

163
00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:17.236
I have something I want to ask you.

164
00:11:18.190 --> 00:11:20.028
Is it okay if I ask?

165
00:11:20.028 --> 00:11:23.028
You've never asked me if you
could ask something before you did.

166
00:11:24.029 --> 00:11:26.927
I change my mind a lot...

167
00:11:27.985 --> 00:11:30.076
and don't take things
very seriously, right?

168
00:11:32.318 --> 00:11:34.395
Who said that?

169
00:11:34.395 --> 00:11:35.993
Just someone.

170
00:11:35.993 --> 00:11:38.038
Someone said that.

171
00:11:38.586 --> 00:11:41.893
You're saying all sorts of crazy things
just because things aren't working out.

172
00:11:43.499 --> 00:11:46.081
That person has the
wrong idea about you.

173
00:11:47.485 --> 00:11:50.105
The problem with you is that
you think too much.

174
00:11:50.105 --> 00:11:52.047
Especially about love.

175
00:11:52.047 --> 00:11:54.481
You can just go where
your heart takes you.

176
00:11:55.999 --> 00:11:59.393
How much longer are you going to be alone
clinging to unsubstantial emotions?

177
00:11:59.393 --> 00:12:00.576
Stop that already.

178
00:12:01.783 --> 00:12:04.416
Stop keeping that man in your heart
if you can't have him.

179
00:12:06.201 --> 00:12:10.432
You're realistic, and yet you're not
when it comes to love.

180
00:12:11.860 --> 00:12:14.326
Right now, your reality is me.

181
00:12:22.560 --> 00:12:25.062
This view is always so amazing,
no matter when I see it.

182
00:12:25.062 --> 00:12:28.206
I hope that we can recoup our
losses for just this month.

183
00:12:28.206 --> 00:12:30.735
"A Star's Life Menu" needs to be a hit.

184
00:12:31.196 --> 00:12:34.139
We'll appeal to the masses with your
face first, before your food.

185
00:12:34.139 --> 00:12:35.908
What's so great about my face?

186
00:12:35.908 --> 00:12:38.539
You're handsome.
And you're miserly.

187
00:12:38.539 --> 00:12:40.507
That is charming to the ladies, too.

188
00:12:40.507 --> 00:12:42.394
What do you mean,
I'm miserly?

189
00:12:42.904 --> 00:12:45.725
You're stingy when it comes to
showing affection to women.

190
00:12:49.134 --> 00:12:52.293
It's because I've been burned
too many times.

191
00:12:52.985 --> 00:12:55.182
By people who have really severe
emotional ups and downs.

192
00:12:55.182 --> 00:12:56.731
It's difficult.

193
00:12:58.807 --> 00:13:01.620
But still, weren't you too
mean to Hong Ah?

194
00:13:02.933 --> 00:13:05.182
I mean, she's a girl, and she really...

195
00:13:05.182 --> 00:13:06.768
and she's no ordinary girl.

196
00:13:06.768 --> 00:13:08.496
And she's prettier than
the average pretty girl.

197
00:13:08.496 --> 00:13:11.196
So if a girl like that comes at you, you
should at least glance her way once.

198
00:13:11.196 --> 00:13:13.413
Why would I, when
I can't take responsibility?

199
00:13:14.090 --> 00:13:16.050
You really are strange.

200
00:13:16.050 --> 00:13:18.988
How could you say such things to me,
when you like Hong Ah?

201
00:13:19.807 --> 00:13:22.250
I don't like her.
I love her.

202
00:13:25.855 --> 00:13:28.187
I'm waiting for her.

203
00:13:29.779 --> 00:13:35.000
To be honest, a part of me was hoping
that you'd be really cruel to her.

204
00:13:35.596 --> 00:13:38.197
But when I see her now,
I feel bad for her.

205
00:13:40.475 --> 00:13:43.364
I'm reminded of my mom
all of the sudden.

206
00:13:43.846 --> 00:13:46.586
I think men and women are
such interesting creatures.

207
00:13:47.121 --> 00:13:50.057
If Hong Ah were a man, I would've ended
things already by beating her up.

208
00:13:54.991 --> 00:13:57.413
I really hope that things
work out for both of us.

209
00:13:57.413 --> 00:13:59.173
I hope "A Star's Life Menu"
becomes popular!

210
00:13:59.173 --> 00:14:01.502
Become successful!
Become successful!

211
00:14:01.502 --> 00:14:03.048
Have you made your decision?

212
00:14:03.048 --> 00:14:04.572
I want to apologize.

213
00:14:04.572 --> 00:14:06.884
You... want to apologize?

214
00:14:06.884 --> 00:14:10.086
- To Chef Ohn Jung Seon.
- I see.

215
00:14:10.086 --> 00:14:11.989
- To be honest, at first...
- Yes?

216
00:14:11.989 --> 00:14:15.267
I thought you only got on the show
because you're a pretty face, like me.

217
00:14:15.267 --> 00:14:17.601
You're just bursting with charisma
until the very end!

218
